This little plasmoid provides a switch to start/stop F.lux / Redshift daemons, and to change location, "temperature" and other configuration variables. See f.lux and Redshift websites for more detailed info.

Developed by Diego Cristina <diegocc100 AT gmail DOT com>
Code under GPLv3 license (see COPYING)

Supported programs:
f.lux for linux: <http://stereopsis.com/flux/>
Redshift for linux: <http://jonls.dk/redshift/>

Requires:
Plasma
Python-KDE4
plasma-scriptengine-python
